{"tid":17230,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[P牌仔] 唔識落highway","createTime":"2016-12-01T17:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T04:57:04.000Z","uid":6166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3db26e5fef72adec153a96e92adf35695f1ab19","tid":17230,"uid":6166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n每次要落highway 匯合右邊d車就好驚<br />\n睇鏡望到右邊不斷有車黎緊，但又識判斷個距離應該繼續比油去/ 停低<br />\n究竟落highway 應該點落？真心求巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 姐係類似呢d位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/015827_c38655412ce0def33bf711352be989dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F015827_c38655412ce0def33bf711352be989dc.jpg&h=b31c9439&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d727a2e7dcdac40846b70983357888df39ce011","tid":17230,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:01:52.000Z","msg":"睇下邊個意志最堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果兩雄相遇...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70245421ccb4f54e336cac55165701972ee72254","tid":17230,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"我今日第一次入都驚到仆利"},{"pid":"a1fe0b39900ac9407d6a7d12dd0ccd8af6681c60","tid":17230,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"膽大心細 一見有位就揸實個信念比油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過撞正一樣信念既就...<br />\n<br />\n師父話 細路岀大路實要讓架啦 多車既 塞既 你咪逐d 逐d 隊岀去"},{"pid":"a3e6da96e1cb418b185ef5d02150912555b8323a","tid":17230,"uid":13416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"45度角大油督出去"},{"pid":"da49352a9b9338499dfc0ba2a09f9b43b0ab5f7d","tid":17230,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c6a4e8fc983a750dda1bb70eec3fe39cd0651e98","tid":17230,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:22:56.000Z","msg":"放油門啦 駁炒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558d3a5eb0da62d13c031f6d1b42e70fa0e3d848","tid":17230,"uid":44908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:24:08.000Z","msg":"怯 你就輸一世。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲通常跑道好長  keep住40 50 行。<br />\n睇通右邊有冇車/距離夠唔夠 大腳油出。快過後面個架咪唔怕人撞你。btw 你唔好撞前面個架播。"},{"pid":"712be00324db498dfd7653aca2b647e13e9bb456","tid":17230,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:29:11.000Z","msg":"落完又唔係叫你即刻簡好條線<br />\n好似新城市依個位有成2-300米<br />\n想轉線咪打燈 遂啲遂啲捱埋去"},{"pid":"29e7c69dd9d5bf3ccd295cdb1bf37dc1a23ae1dc","tid":17230,"uid":23404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:51:50.000Z","msg":"考試就話一定要讓啫<br />\n屌，出到去洗撚讓咩⋯⋯下下讓我唔撚洗行啦<br />\n<br />\n比考肥過我唔讓車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0bbac49ee7e3529c77e36d70fdda62111bd95b","tid":17230,"uid":14860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:16:44.000Z","msg":"由準備入嗰一刻留意住啲車<br />\n調整自己既車速去配合嗰個車與車之間既空隙<br />\n之後定速或者俾少少油就入到"},{"pid":"0f53af34df58724ce26a7cd743c2d973d0f7e5ac","tid":17230,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"無得答......<br />\n睇你識唔識用哂架車性能，得你一個架車輕，後面架車遠d米落多d油，快d上60km/h <br />\n架車多人或者重你慢慢等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdcc7258b3e0d0593e1ed062f1a9c1179889f90","tid":17230,"uid":2543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:31:41.000Z","msg":"有時真係要等好耐先入到線。<br />\n但唔好心急，有信心先入線。<br />\n出多幾次就自然識。"},{"pid":"c884147470adcecdb7888779e4df6ef0f0cd10d0","tid":17230,"uid":28685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"配合大路車速 <br />\n揾車同車中間入"},{"pid":"23546fac1b697356e4a8c121752b967a3e86c563","tid":17230,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:10:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43c38702e3f89708d19ead647806d17d0e45c320","tid":17230,"uid":18363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"自覺夠位就果斷比油去<br />\n沙田個段車速都唔算快<br />\n觀塘繞道落九龍灣方向個段仲快"},{"pid":"bbeeedaa1809df665e9e33a106c05af5c4289b5a","tid":17230,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"即係入Highway?<br />\n呢個位又真係幾多車既, 都無計, 慢慢睇準出去<br />\n記得留意下後車既車速, 就算勁遠, 但好快沖緊過黎, 都可能要等等<br />\n一出到去就唔好慢車, 要比油去架啦<br />\n<br />\n比人閃同呠十幾次就會掌握到架啦<br />\n<br />\np牌最緊要淡定同打燈"},{"pid":"3c14ca986257f8fd86cf935d6e02efb6ce01aa1e","tid":17230,"uid":28685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比油抽頭，done</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比油抽頭唔係唔得 出左去唔好縮油<br />\n好撚多人地板油夾硬出都算 <br />\n出左去又驚地板油太快踩brake<br />\n真係響horn響到佢化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00986f5b61c4aa3b7f147f0d35046a2d4442f5fd","tid":17230,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"怯，你就輸1世"},{"pid":"b6df3d37dfff7446ac92abdeeb0d2d34ef58c4ec","tid":17230,"uid":47023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"咁上下彈出去，過晒線就係神仙"},{"pid":"b33873dec5b996cde2bb2565e893aa0886dc4529","tid":17230,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"夠膽比油多數出到"},{"pid":"6d84cdd0f8a4bfa4af3fd6f3875a1389a77da6b7","tid":17230,"uid":16471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"地板油出啦"},{"pid":"03883b7f55ef1d6c630b0778c998d841948919f1","tid":17230,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"可以呢就盡量唔好停車<br />\n你車速同車流差不多，其實就有時間對返個空隙嘅<br />\n<br />\n如果前面有車都出唔倒你要焗停嘅<br />\n等<br />\n無必要怕柒夾硬出<br />\n你知啦，慢線係大車，收唔切真係分分鍾成個屋苑搵你填命<br />\n<br />\n利：<br />\n有P仔阻撚住個路口一定怒砵"},{"pid":"9edf31a14b0abcb4765965ac124e9284505750d4","tid":17230,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"夠位就比油出去，唔夠位/有車推緊上黎，咪讓人過，再跟佢 pat pat出，多車就等等啦"},{"pid":"0e7a270195991251b74041476c8df35985eb7a81","tid":17230,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"出緊嘅時候記住同時望側鏡同前面<br />\n唔係你一路出，點知前面停咗係度<br />\n一嘢就撞埋落人哋個尾度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b868670a2bb3c76ebec7023f2a147d26e9c5f4","tid":17230,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"一落去就打住個右燈 望下有冇車 有車黎又唔近但又唔知快定慢就開窗舉個手和住油去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76df4e1120a1bc7c8a06697552792d4961331a6","tid":17230,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"收一收油出，唔好停死喺度"},{"pid":"baa8a04e8023fd1d70f1f3e5e5c7a2c6fd281d75","tid":17230,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n每次要落highway 匯合右邊d車就好驚<br />\n睇鏡望到右邊不斷有車黎緊，但又識判斷個距離應該繼續比油去/ 停低<br />\n究竟落highway 應該點落？真心求巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 姐係類似呢d位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/015827_c38655412ce0def33bf711352be989dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F015827_c38655412ce0def33bf711352be989dc.jpg&h=b31c9439&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一般係未入影線就打右燈<br />\n然後用返相合既車速, 即係出面幾多你大慨再慢DD<br />\n然後如果有車喺盲位/平排/稍前半車位 就收一收油讓, 如果冇就出得"},{"pid":"10ffdaebb60eafa1c33e887b668055eef7925075","tid":17230,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"望住跟你後面架車<br />\n佢抽頭岀嗰陣同佢一齊抽<br />\n仲有佢幫你頂住highway啲車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果車多到要攝岀去嘅就加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684618720b32ccd3a74d3861694e27a903e26d09","tid":17230,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:43:09.000Z","msg":"你試下行中隧挑戰膽量"},{"pid":"08e82f4654ca8570ef3233355458403791601218","tid":17230,"uid":22135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"判斷速度就係睇鏡架車距離係越來越近<br />\n定唔郁<br />\n定越來越遠"},{"pid":"45b9a94d6b44be28fddd25133a46f31b76af98de","tid":17230,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"有冇教下點過紅隧收費站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49720f36106d82a31165558fbe156773ee237250","tid":17230,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:02:31.000Z","msg":"有啲車大油加速都好慢，所以堅要睇樓主揸咩車"},{"pid":"7a2fd950921584a125fed71c1b5b715dde1deaf8","tid":17230,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"我p牌果陣都好撚驚（依家都仲驚驚哋）<br />\n博好心司機唯了"},{"pid":"b7a5a37b6adc8bf3f40d20b2a371e46782ecb78c","tid":17230,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇教下點過紅隧收費站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慢慢行<br />\n拉鍊式咁一架一架zip<br />\n熟路嘅入定最靚嗰條線<br />\n等人zip你，唔係你zip人<br />\n真係唔掂嘅開窗舉手俾個五"},{"pid":"46dabb4ff00175001dbabc979dd108db15b7f870","tid":17230,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇教下點過紅隧收費站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慢慢行<br />\n拉鍊式咁一架一架zip<br />\n熟路嘅入定最靚嗰條線<br />\n等人zip你，唔係你zip人<br />\n真係唔掂嘅開窗舉手俾個五</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實紅隧一啲都唔難行吖"},{"pid":"aa9c941df14aa062368cf927efa0ebca6b01c32a","tid":17230,"uid":40658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"你揸錢七就等下位啦<br />\n你揸跑車就咁剷出去就得<br />\n香港地九成人會禮讓靚車"},{"pid":"dd00408c146d9b71ee06e3e40c0ccc39c8294fd2","tid":17230,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:11:17.000Z","msg":"駕駛學院出黎？<br />\n學車果陣師傅已經要我揸晒太子道，界限街，亞皆老街，公主道同窩打老道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望住右鏡先收油，見冇車就即比油去，有車就睇夠唔夠三四個車位喺佢前面，唔夠就先讓佢過，等佢過左就比油出"},{"pid":"91e49916678e0cd38c5b85b7e79a406ebc56322f","tid":17230,"uid":2090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出緊嘅時候記住同時望側鏡同前面<br />\n唔係你一路出，點知前面停咗係度<br />\n一嘢就撞埋落人哋個尾度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次就係差d咁奶左野<br />\n好彩屋企人叫住我 即刻dup 死左先冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba4aa7cba488d4ad798bdd70dcb2fa00fa5388b","tid":17230,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"一腳地板油出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b10f2b1b745d98ac6819fb8c1eeabc0e861f5b","tid":17230,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駕駛學院出黎？<br />\n學車果陣師傅已經要我揸晒太子道，界限街，亞皆老街，公主道同窩打老道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望住右鏡先收油，見冇車就即比油去，有車就睇夠唔夠三四個車位喺佢前面，唔夠就先讓佢過，等佢過左就比油出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔關駕院事<br />\n我2001 年有牌到而家1分都冇俾人扣過<br />\n架車連花痕都冇條<br />\n咪又係駕院"},{"pid":"b7c8bc3bbc1689b2d9ab2bfb6954b029bfc8f96b","tid":17230,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你揸錢七就等下位啦<br />\n你揸跑車就咁剷出去就得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港地九成人會禮讓靚車</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd852dafbeeebe06cd33ab7e8f9ea429623a92d8","tid":17230,"uid":2090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你揸錢七就等下位啦<br />\n你揸跑車就咁剷出去就得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港地九成人會禮讓靚車</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03504d62c87f9d00cfc740301f3d30c03cbe3bbf","tid":17230,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你揸錢七就等下位啦<br />\n你揸跑車就咁剷出去就得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港地九成人會禮讓靚車</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下係咪星期六，日或者係咪的士，小巴佬<br />\n堆weekend driver<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec7a263f9a4a1f2f41536ca3b3bd394607ed0c0","tid":17230,"uid":36661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:21:24.000Z","msg":"一二一二咪隊出去咯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一二一二隻腳啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"691be9e3a56aeecc5a77ff230540565340a5eb38","tid":17230,"uid":40731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\np00"},{"pid":"8bafc164d4ad1ce80e6821742a0b20c7e98faf20","tid":17230,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>駕駛學院出黎？<br />\n學車果陣師傅已經要我揸晒太子道，界限街，亞皆老街，公主道同窩打老道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望住右鏡先收油，見冇車就即比油去，有車就睇夠唔夠三四個車位喺佢前面，唔夠就先讓佢過，等佢過左就比油出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔關駕院事<br />\n我2001 年有牌到而家1分都冇俾人扣過<br />\n架車連花痕都冇條<br />\n咪又係駕院</blockquote><br />\n咪係, 關咩事, 學車, 會唔會行70先<br />\n你掛住學牌, 可以睇定d先出, 後面正常都理解<br />\n但係你而家掛p或無野掛行出街<br />\n遲遲都唔出, 就比人呠到你暈<br />\n<br />\n經驗啦, 淡定同唔怕比人呠, 慢慢你就掌握到"},{"pid":"d2ecc8ea9650c4fa1d75437fc985c87dbe0bb4d2","tid":17230,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一二一二咪隊出去咯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一二一二隻腳啊</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實到宜家都未明咩叫一二一二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8550d82d24f7e5cf30dcb82f418ca322af169133","tid":17230,"uid":12497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:51:13.000Z","msg":"有次爭d俾架拖頭撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5005e242a5403d26487b1e77363285779b86e9d9","tid":17230,"uid":39835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"驚就停，無得夾硬黎<br />\n<br />\n通常大路有司機見到你咁慘會收慢俾你出，你感覺到架"}]}